{"tid":492063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天有眼 裝修狗］裝修公司「先動工後報價」　海關拘董事職員","createTime":"2017-12-07T06:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T07:03:41.000Z","uid":76713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25269ff69b35c7e9d0cf0e4e3b1569e06a7e2d29","tid":492063,"uid":76713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T06:54:05.000Z","msg":"海關早前接獲市民報案，指光顧尖沙咀柯士甸道一間裝修公司時，有人疑使用不良營商手法，施工期間再自行追加工程，並以「先動工，後報價」方式要求找數，案件涉款約100多萬港元。海關經深入調查後採取行動，今晨到該裝修公司搜查，拘捕1名董事及1名職員，2人涉嫌以不良營商手法銷售服務，懷疑觸犯《商品說明條例》，海關正進一步調查事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/145256_3ddacea662f70defff75aef5c527e83a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F145256_3ddacea662f70defff75aef5c527e83a.jpg&h=433ad91e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/145258_21a59677ecf8598f0b63fab5a49e4f77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F145258_21a59677ecf8598f0b63fab5a49e4f77.jpg&h=dc67e907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾多人一世人買得一次樓 <br />\n咁樣呃人 正仆街 <br />\n天有眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161a3e81751ce867c22b18326eab49e1c663c22d","tid":492063,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"有背景就冇事啦"}]}